        INNER JOIN `Permissions` AS `p` ON `f`.`KeyId` = `p`.`FunctionId`
        INNER JOIN `Roles` AS `r` ON `p`.`RoleId` = `r`.`Id`
        WHERE (`r`.`Name` IN ('test') AND (`f`.`KeyId` = @__functionId_1)) AND (`p`.`CanRead` = TRUE))
    THEN TRUE ELSE FALSE
END" (0723d8ff)
